# Audio
XF86Audio{Play,Next,Prev}
    playerctl {play-pause,next,previous}

XF86Audio{Mute,RaiseVolume,LowerVolume}
    amixer sset Master {toggle,1%+,1%-}

shift + XF86Audio{RaiseVolume,LowerVolume}
    amixer sset Master {15%+,15%-}

